                <div className="p-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-indigo-800 rounded-2xl text-white shadow-xl shadow-indigo-100">
                  <Network className="w-8 h-8" />
                </div>
                涨停题材梯队审计 (Ladder Audit)
